reviewText: ELEMENTS OF CLASSIC MUSICAL CHRISTMAS SPECIALS, BUT WITH MODERN UPDATES. HIGHLY AND DIVERSELY TALENTED MUSICAL FAMILY. SHOW MOVES ALONG AT A GOOD PACE, ALL AGES GET INTO THE ACT, FROM INFANTS TO GRANDMA AND GRANDPA. NOTHING REMOTELY OBJECTIONABLE TO ANYONE OF ANY AGE, A HIDDEN GEM YOU PROBABLY NEVER HAVE SEEN, NOT OVEREXPOSED OR WORN OUT. WOULD RECOMMEND TO ANYONE LOOKING FOR MUSICAL FAMILY CHRISTMAS SPECIALS !

If you've seen the Duttons, this is the show you loved! If you haven't seen the Duttons you should make plans to visit Branson, Missouri. They are the best entertainers in Branson and it comes through on their videos. This is a fantastic family experience!

Good sound and picture and just old time fun and dance.  I would recommend this to anyone who wants a holiday special they could enjoy year after year.  Good clean intertainment and what a handsome family.
